5000|$|Tax Fairness Oregon is {{the largest}} tax {{fairness}} organization in the U.S. state of Oregon. Its mission is to [...] "reform <b>our</b> <b>tax</b> code so that it serves the common good, not special interests." [...] It tries to shape tax policy by monitoring and evaluating tax concepts, identifying and analyzing critical bills, testifying at legislative hearings and meeting with legislators, raising awareness of tax issues through media outreach, and building coalitions with partner organizations.|$|R
